lder FGK stars. A change in $\\alpha$ in the tachocline dynamo generates the\nfundamentally different $P_{\\rm cyc}/P_{\\rm rot}$-Ro relationship.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2023 10:54:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-16"}
