ar contours and variable depths. The\noptimized geometry differed from conventional ridge filters as it was\narbitrarily set by the optimizer. This kind of range modulators can be directly\nadded in the CT for dose computation and is well suited for 3D printing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2023 14:26:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-16"}
